  <scopecontent id="aspace_b1d6404bdd0413b540a975e6c32c8e3c">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Daily, monthly, and yearly records of the operation of the railroad, including account books, letter books and correspondence, blueprints of construction and rights of way, company stock, schedules, tariffs, coupons, state, interstate, and federal reports, tickets, and excursion handbills.</p>  </scopecontent>
